reviewText: timely delivery as promised. Excellent product with available choice of dual subtitles at the same time among choices of korean, English and Chinese. A coming of age film in the competitive arena of Olympic athletes. Good production!
I really liked this movie, has two of my favorite Korean actors in it. The quality of the DVD was great.
I loved this movie. The young actors were amazing...will follow their careers from now on...Such a sweet and funny story...
